    {
      "id": "custom-node-pattern-note-shape",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Pattern Shape",
      "position": {
        "x": 2060,
        "y": -40
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Pattern Shape\n\n## Host renderer owns\n- generic control button rendering\n- control placement and slots\n- theming and interaction polish\n- dispatch into actions / scripts / event bus\n\n## Node class owns\n- `node.web` / `editor.web` views\n- control declarations\n- event reactions\n- named scripts or action contracts\n- custom state and visible transitions\n\n## Immediate next move\n- add interior host-rendered control placement to `DynamicViewNode`\n- then restyle bootstrap using that slot",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
